title: Circular
title-note: University of Arkansas agriculture/cooperative extension service
additional-notes: The exact name of the issuer of this University of Arkansas circular has varied somewhat over time, but generally includes 'Agricultural Extension Service' or 'Cooperative Extension Service'.

Some issues of this series have distinctive titles.  Before concluding that such an issue is in the public domain, search for book renewals under its distinctive title. We have not systematically searched individual issue titles.
